  <div class="sb_box br-bg">
    <h3 class="right_title">
      <div class="position">当前位置：<a href="/" title="首页">首页</a> &gt; <a href="/about/?2.html">潍博之信</a>&gt; <a href="/list/?3_1.html">规章制度</a></div>
      <span>规章制度</span> </h3>
    <div class="clear"></div>
    <div class="active" id="shownews">
      <h1 class="title">第八章  文创研发</h1>
      <div class="editor"><p><strong><span style="font-family: 宋体;font-size: 19px"><span style="font-family:宋体">第一条</span></span></strong><span style=";font-family:宋体;font-size:19px">&nbsp;&nbsp;<span style="font-family:宋体">在坚持传统、时尚、便民原则的基础上，整合博物馆与设计界跨领域合作优势，开拓文创产品研发新路径，将创意思维转化为实际生产制作，不断提升本馆文创产品的品质与内涵，积极打造具有</span>“文物元素、博物馆元素、潍坊元素”三重核心要义的文创品牌。</span></p><p><strong><span style="font-family: 宋体;font-size: 19px"><span style="font-family:宋体">第二条</span></span></strong><span style=";font-family:宋体;font-size:19px">&nbsp;&nbsp;</span><strong><span style="font-family: 宋体;font-size: 19px"><span style="font-family:宋体">文创产品研发原则</span></span></strong></p><p><span style=";font-family:宋体;font-size:19px">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;<span style="font-family:宋体">一、展现博物馆自身特色，具有高度的形象识别性。</span></span></p><p><span style=";font-family:宋体;font-size:19px">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;<span style="font-family:宋体">二、多样化设计，满足不同观众的多元化需求。</span></span></p><p><span style=";font-family:宋体;font-size:19px">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;<span style="font-family:宋体">三、注重文创产品开发的原创性、系列性。</span></span></p><p><span style=";font-family:宋体;font-size:19px">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;<span style="font-family:宋体">四、实现创意价值，打造知名品牌。</span></span></p><p><strong><span style="font-family: 宋体;font-size: 19px"><span style="font-family:宋体">第三条</span></span></strong><span style=";font-family:宋体;font-size:19px">&nbsp;&nbsp;</span><strong><span style="font-family: 宋体;font-size: 19px"><span style="font-family:宋体">文创产品机构设置</span></span></strong></p><p><span style=";font-family:宋体;font-size:19px">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;<span style="font-family:宋体">一、馆学术委员会负责文创产品研发的审查。</span></span></p><p><span style=";font-family:宋体;font-size:19px">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;<span style="font-family:宋体">二、组织成立专门的文创产品研发团队，负责文创产品的设计研发、管理、营销等工作。</span></span></p><p><span style=";font-family:宋体;font-size:19px">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;<span style="font-family:宋体">三、特聘具有文创研发技能的文博专家、非物质文化遗产继承人、技艺精湛的工匠等为名誉馆员，增强文创产品研发的综合力量。</span></span></p><p><strong><span style="font-family: 宋体;font-size: 19px"><span style="font-family:宋体">第四条</span></span></strong><span style=";font-family:宋体;font-size:19px">&nbsp;&nbsp;</span><strong><span style="font-family: 宋体;font-size: 19px"><span style="font-family:宋体">文创产品类别</span></span></strong></p><p><span style=";font-family:宋体;font-size:19px">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;<span style="font-family:宋体">一、典藏复制品。</span></span></p><p><span style=";font-family:宋体;font-size:19px">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;<span style="font-family:宋体">二、出版品。</span></span></p><p><span style=";font-family:宋体;font-size:19px">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;<span style="font-family:宋体">三、各类纪念品。</span></span></p><p><strong><span style="font-family: 宋体;font-size: 19px"><span style="font-family:宋体">第五条</span></span></strong><span style=";font-family:宋体;font-size:19px">&nbsp;&nbsp;</span><strong><span style="font-family: 宋体;font-size: 19px"><span style="font-family:宋体">文创产品研发模式</span></span></strong></p><p style="text-indent:38px"><span style=";font-family:宋体;font-size:19px"><span style="font-family:宋体">在确保公益目标、保护好国家文物、做强主业</span></span><span style=";font-family:宋体;font-size:19px"><span style="font-family:宋体">的</span></span><span style=";font-family:宋体;font-size:19px"><span style="font-family:宋体">前提下，依托馆藏资源，采取合作、授权、独立开发等</span></span><span style=";font-family:宋体;font-size:19px"><span style="font-family:宋体">模式研</span></span><span style=";font-family:宋体;font-size:19px"><span style="font-family:宋体">发文化创意产品</span></span><span style=";font-family:宋体;font-size:19px"><span style="font-family:宋体">。</span></span></p><p style="text-indent:37px"><span style=";font-family:宋体;font-size:19px">1、独立研发模式，即依靠本馆文创人员，深挖馆藏文物资源文化内涵，独立设计、研发具有博物馆特色、潍坊特色的文创产品，使博物馆与社会大众紧密连结，让文物真正活起来，让观众真正把“博物馆”带回家。</span></p><p style="text-indent:37px"><span style=";font-family:宋体;font-size:19px">2、合作研发模式，即以本馆馆藏文物资源为基础，与其他博物馆、学校、企业研发力量、设计团队联合推进文创研发，各取所长，凝心聚力，研发出充分反映馆藏历史、文化、艺术价值的衍生品。</span></p><p><span style=";font-family:宋体;font-size:19px">3、授权研发模式，即将本馆馆藏文物资源衍生品的研发，实行艺术设计授权，由专业设计团队执行设计策略，由本馆严格把关、确保品质。</span></p><p><br/></p><script src="/inc/AspCms_VisitsAdd.asp?id=472"></script></div>
      
      <div class="met_page">上一条：<a href="/content/?471.html">第九章  组织人事</a>&nbsp;&nbsp;下一条：<a href="/content/?473.html">第七章  学术研究</a></div>
    </div>
